reviews: Great material, elasticity and price. Exactly what i was looking for.

review_title: Good size and it does the job
reviews:
I got this for my 7 yr old son, who likes Lego. Good size and it does the job. I understand that I am paying extra for the Lego Brand, but i still think Its over priced for such a basic alarm clock. Has a simple beeping sound for the alarm and It would be nice if it had alternative alarm sounds and a way to adjust the volume.
If the Lego brand isn't important to you or loved ones, you can get alot more bang for your buck else where.
